1
00:00:12,333 --> 00:00:14,541
TOKONG SHEN-LUNG

2
00:00:14,625 --> 00:00:17,666
AIR SHEN-LUNG

3
00:00:17,750 --> 00:00:19,958
KEHIDUPAN ABADI

4
00:00:20,041 --> 00:00:22,583
KEHIDUPAN

5
00:00:22,666 --> 00:00:25,375
TOKONG SHEN-LUNG

6
00:00:27,583 --> 00:00:29,166
- Inikah orangnya?
- Ya.

7
00:00:30,208 --> 00:00:32,791
Bukan setakat tipu duit,
kau main bini aku!

8
00:00:33,458 --> 00:00:34,833
Dasar penunggang agama.

9
00:00:34,916 --> 00:00:35,750
Jom!

10
00:00:49,875 --> 00:00:53,083
Ajal kau dah hampir,
Putera Mahkota Shen-Lung.

11
00:00:53,875 --> 00:00:57,708
Aku boleh selamatkan kau.
Tapi kau perlu bayar harganya.

12
00:00:59,291 --> 00:01:00,750
Peganglah tangan aku.

13
00:01:01,750 --> 00:01:04,166
Aku boleh ubah takdir kau.

14
00:01:28,333 --> 00:01:31,125
AGENT FROM ABOVE

15
00:01:32,958 --> 00:01:36,458
MENGUMPUL ROH

16
00:01:36,958 --> 00:01:38,958
PASAR DONGFENG

17
00:01:58,666 --> 00:02:00,875
Jemput makan, semua!

18
00:02:03,541 --> 00:02:05,333
- Terima kasih.
- Wah, banyaknya.

19
00:02:05,916 --> 00:02:07,416
Hebatnya jamuan ini.

20
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:09,458
- Sedapnya!
- Betul.

21
00:02:09,541 --> 00:02:11,750
- Memang sedap.
- Makanlah puas-puas.

22
00:02:11,833 --> 00:02:14,583
Selamat datang.
Saya boleh sediakan apa saja.

23
00:02:14,666 --> 00:02:16,083
- Baiknya.
- Ambilkan satu.

24
00:02:16,166 --> 00:02:19,833
- Cukup untuk semua. Makanlah.
- Baiknya awak.

25
00:02:19,916 --> 00:02:22,000
Ada pencuci mulut dan lauk di sini.

26
00:02:22,083 --> 00:02:23,041
Besarnya.

27
00:02:26,375 --> 00:02:29,291
Hai, saya Mei-na.
Selamat datang ke tempat ini.

28
00:02:29,375 --> 00:02:33,083
Hai, saya Wang Hsiao-ming.
Minat nak kahwin dengan hantu tak?

29
00:02:45,791 --> 00:02:46,750
Wang Hsiao-ming.

30
00:02:50,708 --> 00:02:51,791
Ada apa?

31
00:02:52,291 --> 00:02:53,291
Pilihlah.

32
00:02:56,291 --> 00:02:58,291
Biar benar?

33
00:03:00,166 --> 00:03:01,375
Baiknya awak.

34
00:03:01,458 --> 00:03:04,833
Yang ini nampak hodoh.
Pakailah sut, baru segak.

35
00:03:04,916 --> 00:03:08,166
Dia pakai apa-apa pun tetap hodoh.

36
00:03:08,250 --> 00:03:11,375
Janganlah begitu, nenek.
Berilah dia galakan.

37
00:03:11,875 --> 00:03:13,083
Ayuh, cubalah pakai.

38
00:03:13,666 --> 00:03:14,791
Sama-sama?

39
00:03:14,875 --> 00:03:18,000
- Salin pakaian?
- Apa? Sama-sama?

40
00:03:18,083 --> 00:03:19,875
- Marilah ikut.
- Cepat.

41
00:03:20,958 --> 00:03:22,666
Han Chieh, nampak Pn. Chiang?

42
00:03:22,750 --> 00:03:25,375
Dia pindah sebelah rumah awak
minggu lepas.

43
00:03:26,791 --> 00:03:30,000
Tapi saya pernah nampak anaknya.
Saya rasa dia pekak.

44
00:03:31,291 --> 00:03:34,250
Mesti hidup Pn. Chiang sukar.

45
00:03:34,833 --> 00:03:38,083
Tak apa. Saya nak jemput dia
makan di restoran saya.

46
00:03:38,708 --> 00:03:41,916
Nanti tegurlah dia apabila ada masa, ya?

47
00:03:48,208 --> 00:03:49,041
Perhatian!

48
00:03:52,541 --> 00:03:54,791
Wah, Wang Hsiao-ming.

49
00:03:54,875 --> 00:03:56,541
Aduhai, Wang Hsiao-ming.

50
00:03:56,625 --> 00:03:58,958
- Ini gaya lama.
- Macam orang tua.

51
00:03:59,041 --> 00:04:00,791
- Taklah.
- Wang Tua Ming.

52
00:04:01,583 --> 00:04:03,916
- Wang Tua Ming.
- Awak nampak bergaya.

53
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:05,750
Walaupun lapar tak bermaya.

54
00:04:07,125 --> 00:04:08,791
Semua orang bergaul mesra.

55
00:04:13,833 --> 00:04:16,250
Mujurlah ada pak cik dan Kak Lo.

56
00:04:18,416 --> 00:04:21,208
Keluarga mereka juga mati
dalam kebakaran itu?

57
00:04:21,291 --> 00:04:22,333
Ya.

58
00:04:23,541 --> 00:04:26,500
Adik Kak Lo serta anak dan cucu pak cik.

59
00:04:28,041 --> 00:04:32,166
Mereka nak tinggal dengan keluarga.
Jadi, saya buka mata ketiga mereka.

60
00:04:34,833 --> 00:04:37,791
Tapi entah kenapa
adik Kak Lo tak pernah muncul.

61
00:04:40,208 --> 00:04:42,041
Harap Kak Lo boleh terima hakikat itu.

62
00:04:45,791 --> 00:04:46,625
Han Chieh.

63
00:04:46,708 --> 00:04:50,166
Muka awak asyik masam,
tapi awak sebenarnya sangat baik.

64
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:58,625
Awak asyik melepak di sini saja.
Awak makan ubat tak?

65
00:04:59,500 --> 00:05:00,500
Mestilah makan.

66
00:05:03,416 --> 00:05:04,791
Han Chieh, senyum.

67
00:05:08,083 --> 00:05:09,083
Awak buat apa?

68
00:05:22,083 --> 00:05:25,166
Chang Min: Seluruh Geng Heilung
dibunuh malam tadi.

69
00:05:25,250 --> 00:05:28,625
Kematian mereka aneh.
Jumpa awak esok. Tolong saya.

70
00:05:30,750 --> 00:05:33,875
LINDUNGI SELURUH KELUARGA

71
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:42,791
Mesti hidup Pn. Chiang sukar.

72
00:05:42,875 --> 00:05:45,250
Nanti tegurlah dia apabila ada masa, ya?

73
00:05:49,083 --> 00:05:52,000
Saya Han Chieh, jiran sebelah.

74
00:05:53,666 --> 00:05:56,666
Awak ejen kayangan
yang Kak Lo sebut itu, bukan?

75
00:06:01,166 --> 00:06:04,958
Semua orang berkumpul di bumbung.
Kak Lo tanya tentang awak.

76
00:06:05,041 --> 00:06:07,583
- Bawalah anak awak sekali.
- Tak payahlah.

77
00:06:07,666 --> 00:06:10,500
Yuan-yuan pekak dan bisu.
Nanti menyusahkan saja.

78
00:06:12,083 --> 00:06:15,750
Saya jumpa dia beberapa hari lalu.
Dia suka melukis.

79
00:06:15,833 --> 00:06:17,000
Budaknya ceria.

80
00:06:41,250 --> 00:06:44,291
- Saya takkan kacau awak lagi.
- Bomoh Han.

81
00:06:44,375 --> 00:06:47,458
Saya dah lama sakit.
Anak saya pula pekak dan bisu.

82
00:06:47,541 --> 00:06:49,958
- Ada cara tak…
- Saya bukan bomoh.

83
00:06:51,708 --> 00:06:53,125
Saya cuma manusia biasa.

84
00:06:55,041 --> 00:06:55,875
Maaf.

85
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,833
ROH SESAT

86
00:07:14,625 --> 00:07:17,625
PUTERA MAHKOTA SHEN LUNG DISIHIR BOMOH
UNTUK BUAT JENAYAH

87
00:07:52,083 --> 00:07:54,708
KEBAKARAN TOKONG, DUA TERBUNUH

88
00:07:54,791 --> 00:07:56,125
TOKONG FENGYUAN

89
00:08:00,541 --> 00:08:02,333
PEMILIK TOKONG DIBUNUH

90
00:08:02,416 --> 00:08:05,833
PENAFIAN LIU KUAN-FU:
"IA TIADA KAITAN DENGAN SAYA"

91
00:08:06,416 --> 00:08:08,666
KEBAKARAN AKIBAT PERTIKAIAN TANAH?

92
00:08:08,750 --> 00:08:10,791
LIU KUAN-FU JAWAB: "MANA BUKTI?"

93
00:08:14,208 --> 00:08:18,166
"MANA BUKTI?"

94
00:08:26,041 --> 00:08:27,791
CHANG MIN

95
00:08:37,333 --> 00:08:38,875
Kenapa tak jawab?

96
00:08:40,166 --> 00:08:42,000
Awak bukan ada berita baik pun.

97
00:08:42,583 --> 00:08:43,416
Hei.

98
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,375
Cuba tengok.

99
00:08:49,166 --> 00:08:50,291
"Raja Syaitan"?

100
00:08:51,625 --> 00:08:54,541
Sebelas ahli Geng Heilung mati
dengan cara pelik.

101
00:08:59,083 --> 00:09:00,458
Chen Chi-sha?

102
00:09:00,958 --> 00:09:04,291
Geng Heilung ramai musuh.
Ini mungkin pembunuhan upahan.

103
00:09:05,083 --> 00:09:09,333
Chen Chi-sha takkan membunuh untuk duit.
Simbol Raja Syaitan pun ada.

104
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:12,708
Ini bukan pergaduhan geng yang biasa.

105
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:22,625
Jika dah susah nanti,
jangan salahkan saya pula.

106
00:09:26,125 --> 00:09:28,208
Saya ada kawan di tokong. Bekas gengster.

107
00:09:28,291 --> 00:09:30,916
Saya nak tanya dia.
Mungkin dia tahu sesuatu.

108
00:09:32,875 --> 00:09:33,708
Silakan.

109
00:09:33,791 --> 00:09:34,875
- Hei, Fu.
- Duduk.

110
00:09:34,958 --> 00:09:37,750
Sekarang awak dah kayakah?
Besarnya tokong awak.

111
00:09:38,250 --> 00:09:40,000
Awak balik ke dunia lamakah?

112
00:09:40,666 --> 00:09:43,541
Taklah. Jangan salah faham.

113
00:09:43,625 --> 00:09:46,458
Saya dah tak menyamar jadi bomoh

114
00:09:46,541 --> 00:09:48,750
dan jual nombor ekor palsu lagi.

115
00:09:48,833 --> 00:09:51,291
Tentang duit derma tokong ini pula,

116
00:09:51,375 --> 00:09:55,000
semuanya pergi kepada badan amal
lepas tolak yuran pengurusan.

117
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:58,708
Saya juga bersihkan pantai,
jamu gelandangan makan.

118
00:10:01,500 --> 00:10:03,416
- Tengok buku akaun.
- Tak perlu.

119
00:10:04,333 --> 00:10:05,875
Saya bukan nak siasat awak.

120
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,375
Awak ada maklumat baru tak?

121
00:10:18,166 --> 00:10:22,000
Ada kawan dari tokong lain bercerita.

122
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:26,500
Geng Heilung baru menang kontrak
projek pembinaan kerajaan 100 juta.

123
00:10:26,583 --> 00:10:29,625
Liu Kuan-fu dan Geng Heilung
ada perjanjian.

124
00:10:29,708 --> 00:10:34,208
Geng Heilung perlu subkontrakkan kerja itu
kepada pembekal Liu Kuan-fu.

125
00:10:34,291 --> 00:10:36,833
Tapi mungkin mereka gaduh
tentang pembahagian untung

126
00:10:36,916 --> 00:10:39,125
lalu Geng Heilung ambil semuanya.

127
00:10:44,333 --> 00:10:49,333
Semua orang tahu mereka lama bersengketa.
Lambat-laun ia akan berlaku juga.

128
00:10:49,416 --> 00:10:53,500
Cuma saya tak sangka
Liu Kuan-fu kejam begitu.

129
00:10:53,583 --> 00:10:54,791
Kejam?

130
00:10:55,916 --> 00:10:57,250
Dia memang kejam pun.

131
00:10:58,333 --> 00:11:01,250
Dulu dia rampas dan bakar
tokong buruk kami.

132
00:11:01,875 --> 00:11:05,750
Untuk rampas tanah keluarga saya,
dia buat saya ketagih dadah

133
00:11:06,750 --> 00:11:08,416
supaya terjerat hutang.

134
00:11:09,416 --> 00:11:10,791
TOKONG FENGYUAN

135
00:11:11,750 --> 00:11:15,125
Kemudian dia suruh cagarkan
geran tanah tokong kepadanya.

136
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:30,333
SIJIL GERAN TANAH

137
00:11:32,291 --> 00:11:33,500
Melutut!

138
00:11:33,583 --> 00:11:35,916
Jelaskan kepada Putera Mahkota Ketiga.

139
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:39,166
Sekarang, syarikat pembinaan kata
tanah tokong kita milik mereka!

140
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:41,500
- Anak derhaka! Nak ayah mati?
- Cukup.

141
00:11:41,583 --> 00:11:43,625
Kau tahu buat masalah saja!

142
00:11:43,708 --> 00:11:44,750
Sudahlah.

143
00:11:51,666 --> 00:11:53,083
Ayah saya tak mengalah,

144
00:11:53,583 --> 00:11:56,125
jadi Liu Kuan-fu bakar seluruh tokong.

145
00:11:56,958 --> 00:11:59,166
- Bagaimana terbakar?
- Barang kita di sana.

146
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:02,916
Ada sesiapa keluar tak?
Api tiba-tiba marak.

147
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,708
Apa kita patut buat?

148
00:12:06,500 --> 00:12:08,875
- Hei!
- Bertenang!

149
00:12:27,583 --> 00:12:29,083
TOKONG FENGYUAN

150
00:12:29,166 --> 00:12:30,291
Akhirnya,

151
00:12:30,791 --> 00:12:35,708
ibu dan ayah saya
tak dapat keluar dari kebakaran itu.

152
00:12:45,875 --> 00:12:49,083
Sampai sekarang,
mereka terseksa di neraka kerana saya.

153
00:12:53,541 --> 00:12:55,500
Putera Mahkota Ketiga
nak saya bunuh hantu.

154
00:12:56,625 --> 00:13:00,291
Tapi jika ada manusia
lebih teruk daripada hantu,

155
00:13:00,375 --> 00:13:02,000
tak salah bunuh dia, bukan?

156
00:13:07,875 --> 00:13:10,000
Saya faham perasaan awak.

157
00:13:10,500 --> 00:13:12,125
Dia tahu perkara yang jadi,

158
00:13:12,208 --> 00:13:14,750
sebab itu dia beri
peluang tebus kesilapan.

159
00:13:14,833 --> 00:13:16,208
Tanggungjawab awak besar.

160
00:13:17,791 --> 00:13:18,791
Merepeklah.

161
00:13:20,125 --> 00:13:21,708
Kenapa awak begini? Hei.

162
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:24,041
Awak tonton filem Marvel?

163
00:13:24,125 --> 00:13:27,708
Awak pernah lihat
Iron Man membunuh secara melulu?

164
00:13:27,791 --> 00:13:30,875
Iron Man pun jadi wira
lepas dia tebus kesilapannya.

165
00:13:30,958 --> 00:13:33,625
Awak sebenarnya adiwira.

166
00:13:33,708 --> 00:13:36,416
Besar kuasa, besarlah tanggungjawabnya.

167
00:13:36,500 --> 00:13:40,041
Jika awak main-main,
awak sama saja macam Liu Kuan-fu.

168
00:13:42,125 --> 00:13:43,708
Jika saya adiwira, awak siapa?

169
00:13:45,625 --> 00:13:46,625
Saya?

170
00:13:49,375 --> 00:13:50,291
Saya yang ini.

171
00:13:56,125 --> 00:13:57,125
Pemandu lori?

172
00:13:59,083 --> 00:14:01,583
Pemandu lori apa? Saya Dr. Strange.

173
00:14:01,666 --> 00:14:04,750
Awak tak tahukah? Dr. Strange. Nampak tak?

174
00:14:04,833 --> 00:14:05,666
Hei.

175
00:14:06,166 --> 00:14:07,000
Hei.

176
00:14:07,500 --> 00:14:10,791
Betul juga, macam pandu lorilah.
Hei, tunggu saya.

177
00:14:18,666 --> 00:14:19,500
Bos.

178
00:14:25,416 --> 00:14:29,541
Bos, Chen Chi-sha minta kita datang
ke tempat terpencil begini.

179
00:14:29,625 --> 00:14:31,041
Apa rancangan dia?

180
00:14:31,708 --> 00:14:32,791
En. Liu.

181
00:14:39,708 --> 00:14:42,041
Semua duitnya ada di sini.

182
00:14:42,125 --> 00:14:43,958
Jika tak bayar pun, aku buat.

183
00:14:44,875 --> 00:14:49,625
Aku nak uji puaka neraka aku.
Geng Heilung memang calon yang sesuai.

184
00:14:53,375 --> 00:14:55,250
Mereka mati dengan tragik.

185
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,333
Duitnya ada di sini.

186
00:14:58,416 --> 00:15:00,916
Mulai sekarang, kita tiada kaitan apa-apa.

187
00:15:01,625 --> 00:15:04,125
Cepatnya kamu nak tinggalkan aku.

188
00:15:05,416 --> 00:15:07,708
Ketika kali pertama kamu jumpa aku,

189
00:15:07,791 --> 00:15:09,833
bukankah kamu kagum dengan aku?

190
00:15:14,416 --> 00:15:16,208
Jangan datang jumpa kami lagi!

191
00:15:16,291 --> 00:15:17,625
- Beri dia…
- Bos.

192
00:15:17,708 --> 00:15:19,125
- Beri duit itu.
- Nah.

193
00:16:12,375 --> 00:16:15,875
Tuan datang sini,
maksudnya hal itu dah selesai?

194
00:16:16,375 --> 00:16:18,625
Aku dah tua. Kemahiran dah berkarat.

195
00:16:22,791 --> 00:16:24,250
Janganlah merendah diri.

196
00:16:27,333 --> 00:16:31,333
Mustahil Raja Syaitan
pilih orang biasa-biasa.

197
00:16:35,333 --> 00:16:39,958
Cara puaka neraka tuan bunuh
ahli Geng Heilung sangat menakutkan.

198
00:16:48,500 --> 00:16:52,125
Dulu aku berpakat dengan Raja Syaitan
untuk balas dendam.

199
00:16:52,958 --> 00:16:54,625
Gengster bunuh keluarga aku.

200
00:16:55,208 --> 00:16:57,041
Mereka ini tak layak hidup.

201
00:16:57,625 --> 00:16:59,041
Tapi sekarang dah lain.

202
00:16:59,666 --> 00:17:03,750
Kau dan Raja Syaitan berpakat
untuk kawal aku, paksa aku membunuh.

203
00:17:04,750 --> 00:17:09,458
Aku tahu aku tak boleh dimaafkan.
Tapi dulu aku tak bunuh orang baik.

204
00:17:10,750 --> 00:17:12,375
Sebagai orang jahat,

205
00:17:12,875 --> 00:17:16,166
aku tahu kejahatan ada banyak wajah.

206
00:17:17,916 --> 00:17:20,750
Tapi kita berbeza.

207
00:17:29,041 --> 00:17:32,000
Sekarang kau nak aku buat apa pula?

208
00:17:44,333 --> 00:17:45,416
CHIANG HUA-CHIH

209
00:17:46,125 --> 00:17:50,208
Berdasarkan carta kelahiran,
penyakit awak dan keadaan anak awak

210
00:17:50,291 --> 00:17:51,666
dah ditakdirkan.

211
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:56,875
Jadi, bolehkah saya ubah takdir saya?

212
00:17:56,958 --> 00:17:59,583
Takdir dah ditentukan
oleh butiran kelahiran.

213
00:18:00,083 --> 00:18:01,083
Ia tak boleh diubah.

214
00:18:11,333 --> 00:18:12,833
Tapi…

215
00:18:13,416 --> 00:18:16,000
Ada cara untuk hapuskan halangan karma.

216
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:17,000
Betulkah?

217
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,416
Bagaimana?

218
00:18:21,208 --> 00:18:22,375
Putera Mahkota Shen-Lung.

219
00:18:27,875 --> 00:18:31,875
Buat apa jadi bomoh palsu?

220
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,833
Jika kau bekerja untuk aku,

221
00:18:35,625 --> 00:18:37,750
aku akan beri semua yang kau nak.

222
00:18:39,333 --> 00:18:40,541
Apa saya perlu buat?

223
00:18:57,000 --> 00:18:58,791
Awak bawa anak awak tak?

224
00:19:00,916 --> 00:19:02,958
- Tuan.
- Ya?

225
00:19:03,458 --> 00:19:04,666
Saya bawa dia.

226
00:19:05,250 --> 00:19:07,958
Sebenarnya,
saya tak beritahu awak tempoh hari

227
00:19:08,666 --> 00:19:12,333
yang rumah awak diselubungi
aura sial yang kuat.

228
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:17,458
Besar kemungkinan
ada orang terdekat yang jejaskan kamu.

229
00:19:19,833 --> 00:19:21,375
Bila anak awak lahir?

230
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,625
Dia lahir pada 17 Mac 2009.

231
00:19:27,833 --> 00:19:32,208
Maknanya hari ke-21, bulan dua,
pada Tahun Lembu kalendar Cina?

232
00:19:32,833 --> 00:19:37,166
Aku perlukan sekumpulan puaka neraka
yang dicipta daripada jiwa hakiki manusia.

233
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:39,958
Cari orang yang butiran lahirnya sepadan…

234
00:19:40,041 --> 00:19:41,500
21 BULAN DUA TAHUN LEMBU

235
00:19:41,583 --> 00:19:42,958
…dan bunuh mereka.

236
00:19:44,958 --> 00:19:46,125
Dengar sini.

237
00:19:46,208 --> 00:19:48,333
Anak awak sebenarnya punca

238
00:19:48,416 --> 00:19:50,458
penyakit awak tak sembuh-sembuh.

239
00:19:51,125 --> 00:19:55,958
Sebab carta lahir kamu berlawanan.
Dia buat awak sakit, awak buat dia bisu.

240
00:19:56,041 --> 00:19:59,583
Sebab itu dia bisu seumur hidup,
awak pun sakit seumur hidup.

241
00:20:00,500 --> 00:20:02,208
Mustahil anak saya puncanya.

242
00:20:02,291 --> 00:20:03,791
Tuan pasti?

243
00:20:03,875 --> 00:20:05,833
Saya pasti.

244
00:20:06,416 --> 00:20:07,625
Apa patut saya buat?

245
00:20:08,208 --> 00:20:10,041
Keluar. Tinggalkan dia di sini.

246
00:20:14,041 --> 00:20:15,750
- Sila keluar.
- Tunggu.

247
00:20:15,833 --> 00:20:18,083
- Apa tuan nak buat pada dia?
- Keluar!

248
00:20:18,166 --> 00:20:21,166
- Yuan-yuan, mari sini!
- Keluar!

249
00:20:21,250 --> 00:20:22,291
- Keluar!
- Yuan-yuan!

250
00:20:24,125 --> 00:20:26,958
Han Chieh, ini pemetik api yang awak nak.

251
00:20:57,416 --> 00:20:59,875
PUTERA MAHKOTA SHEN LUNG
BAHAYAKAN ORANG

252
00:21:01,083 --> 00:21:02,291
Nama dia lagi.

253
00:21:02,958 --> 00:21:03,791
Apa?

254
00:21:11,125 --> 00:21:13,625
Ini kali ketiga nama itu muncul bulan ini.

255
00:21:13,708 --> 00:21:17,625
Pertama, tipu wang dan seks.
Kedua, disihir oleh bomoh.

256
00:21:18,166 --> 00:21:22,375
Tapi awak tak peduli pun.
Sekarang, keadaan semakin teruk.

257
00:21:24,125 --> 00:21:24,958
Salah saya pula?

258
00:21:25,708 --> 00:21:29,041
Saya ada banyak kerja.
Bagaimana nak buat serentak?

259
00:21:32,750 --> 00:21:35,000
Saya tak boleh tangkap semua bomoh palsu.

260
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:38,083
Dahlah awak nak saya halang Raja Syaitan.
Saya manusia, bukan dewa.

261
00:21:38,166 --> 00:21:41,916
Diri sendiri pun tak terjaga.
Kenapa saya nak peduli semua ini? Sial.

262
00:21:43,541 --> 00:21:45,291
Han Chieh, awak nak ke mana?

263
00:21:58,041 --> 00:21:59,041
Yuan-yuan?

264
00:21:59,750 --> 00:22:00,791
Han Chieh.

265
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:02,458
Kenapa dia…

266
00:22:27,250 --> 00:22:28,208
Siapa buli awak?

267
00:22:29,875 --> 00:22:30,833
Mana ibu awak?

268
00:22:39,875 --> 00:22:41,958
Saya nak pergi neraka. Tolong saya.

269
00:22:42,041 --> 00:22:42,875
Saya?

270
00:22:47,791 --> 00:22:49,166
Saya dah selalu pergi.

271
00:22:49,833 --> 00:22:52,333
Saya akan pengsankan diri dengan guna kad.

272
00:22:56,583 --> 00:22:59,666
Tiga minit selepas saya pengsan,
mainkan muzik.

273
00:23:01,750 --> 00:23:02,666
Renjat saya.

274
00:23:12,041 --> 00:23:13,041
Jangan gagal.

275
00:23:57,083 --> 00:24:00,333
BARAT

276
00:24:25,333 --> 00:24:26,416
Pn. Chiang.

277
00:24:31,125 --> 00:24:32,166
Apa jadi?

278
00:24:32,875 --> 00:24:36,166
Saya tak jumpa Yuan-yuan.
Saya cari merata-rata.

279
00:24:36,250 --> 00:24:38,083
Dia mati sebelum saya.

280
00:24:39,083 --> 00:24:40,375
Saya tak jumpa dia.

281
00:24:40,458 --> 00:24:41,666
Mana jiwa hakikinya?

282
00:24:43,875 --> 00:24:45,458
Saya tak tahu.

283
00:24:45,541 --> 00:24:48,375
Dia tak boleh turun ke sini
atau menjelma semula tanpanya.

284
00:24:49,250 --> 00:24:50,083
Ini kerja siapa?

285
00:24:53,416 --> 00:24:54,916
Putera Mahkota Shen-Lung.

286
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:57,750
Buka pintu! Yuan-yuan!

287
00:24:58,791 --> 00:25:00,583
Yuan-yuan!

288
00:25:01,250 --> 00:25:02,375
Yuan-yuan!

289
00:25:52,125 --> 00:25:54,041
Saya buat anak saya dibunuh

290
00:25:55,000 --> 00:25:57,416
dan saya pun dibunuh.

291
00:25:59,708 --> 00:26:02,000
- Mana bomoh itu?
- Di tokongnya.

292
00:26:22,000 --> 00:26:23,166
BARAT

293
00:26:23,250 --> 00:26:24,625
Masa dah tamat.

294
00:26:25,916 --> 00:26:28,583
- Awak nak ke mana?
- Nak cari bedebah itu.

295
00:26:35,833 --> 00:26:38,083
Bagaimana awak nak ke sana?

296
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:42,541
- Awak masih hidup?
- Sekarang ini, saya mati.

297
00:26:50,666 --> 00:26:52,083
Siapa awak sebenarnya?

298
00:26:54,166 --> 00:26:55,708
Pekerja Putera Mahkota Ketiga.

299
00:27:02,958 --> 00:27:04,375
Kenapa voltan tinggi sangat?

300
00:27:05,583 --> 00:27:08,083
Awak tak beri arahan betul-betul.

301
00:27:09,750 --> 00:27:10,583
Ambilkan baju.

302
00:27:15,166 --> 00:27:17,291
Biji teratai di dalam peti sejuk.

303
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:35,500
Beritahu Chang Min,
ada pembunuhan di Tokong Shenlung.

304
00:27:35,583 --> 00:27:36,583
Awak nak ke mana?

305
00:27:37,875 --> 00:27:39,500
Nak selesaikan perhitungan.

306
00:27:43,500 --> 00:27:45,750
GELUNG QIANKUN

307
00:27:59,125 --> 00:28:01,208
TOKONG SHEN-LUNG

308
00:28:18,500 --> 00:28:19,875
Keluar, semua!

309
00:28:22,458 --> 00:28:25,250
Wah, ejen kayangan
Putera Mahkota Ketiga datang.

310
00:28:25,333 --> 00:28:26,458
Maaf tak buat persiapan.

311
00:28:26,541 --> 00:28:28,208
Saya beri awak peluang.

312
00:28:28,291 --> 00:28:30,791
Serahkan jiwa hakiki itu jika nak selamat.

313
00:28:31,375 --> 00:28:33,500
Putera Mahkota Ketiga memang nakal.

314
00:28:33,583 --> 00:28:36,458
Ejen dia pun cuma samseng
yang cakap besar.

315
00:28:36,541 --> 00:28:37,791
Baiklah.

316
00:28:37,875 --> 00:28:41,541
Saya bukan setakat nak pukul,
saya nak belasah cukup-cukup.

317
00:29:28,666 --> 00:29:29,875
Putera Mahkota Ketiga!

318
00:29:29,958 --> 00:29:31,791
Putera Mahkota Ketiga!

319
00:29:48,583 --> 00:29:51,291
Suruh Putera Mahkota
datang kutip mayat kau.

320
00:30:18,291 --> 00:30:21,583
Awak ingat awak kuat?
Siapa suruh awak lawan cakap saya?

321
00:30:22,375 --> 00:30:25,375
Lawan bomoh palsu pun kalah.
Itu pun tak laratkah?

322
00:30:25,458 --> 00:30:26,708
Awak ingat saya suka?

323
00:30:28,333 --> 00:30:31,166
- Mana kad yang saya beri?
- Saya dah guna.

324
00:30:32,250 --> 00:30:33,375
Awak tak nampakkah?

325
00:30:39,000 --> 00:30:41,750
Kad yang awak beri
cuma mainan bagi mereka.

326
00:30:42,291 --> 00:30:43,583
Jadi, awak datang mengadu?

327
00:30:44,166 --> 00:30:48,041
Jika saya dilarang merokok atau minum,
setidaknya berilah barang yang bagus.

328
00:30:52,708 --> 00:30:54,833
Saya larang awak merokok atau minum.

329
00:30:55,333 --> 00:30:57,708
Tapi awak guna Gelung Qiankun
untuk nyalakan rokok.

330
00:30:58,208 --> 00:30:59,500
Jangan lupa,

331
00:31:00,000 --> 00:31:04,583
lebih baik barang yang saya beri,
lebih sakit awak nanti.

332
00:31:05,625 --> 00:31:06,875
Saya tak takut pun.

333
00:31:13,750 --> 00:31:15,208
Saya beri satu lagi.

334
00:31:23,791 --> 00:31:26,291
Saya dah kata, ia tak berkesan pada dia.

335
00:31:26,791 --> 00:31:28,208
Kad ini lebih istimewa.

336
00:31:30,666 --> 00:31:32,166
Dah puas tumbuk?

337
00:31:34,041 --> 00:31:35,333
Giliran saya pula.

338
00:33:19,833 --> 00:33:23,916
Kami dah lama pantau bomoh palsu ini,
tapi tak jumpa bukti jenayahnya.

339
00:33:24,000 --> 00:33:26,500
Baguslah Putera Mahkota Ketiga
beri amaran.

340
00:33:26,583 --> 00:33:28,500
Kali ini, dia takkan terlepas.

341
00:33:30,666 --> 00:33:32,125
Saya patut siasat lebih awal.

342
00:33:37,291 --> 00:33:39,666
TOKONG SHEN-LUNG

343
00:33:56,166 --> 00:33:58,000
PASAR DONGFENG

344
00:34:45,250 --> 00:34:48,625
Yuan-yuan, carilah ibu awak sekarang.

345
00:35:18,416 --> 00:35:21,625
QIAN, XUN, KAN

346
00:35:36,416 --> 00:35:38,458
AYAH: UJIAN DAH TAMAT? BILA SAMPAI RUMAH?

347
00:35:38,541 --> 00:35:41,166
SAYA DAH NAK SAMPAI

348
00:41:02,708 --> 00:41:04,416
Terjemahan sari kata oleh MMA

